{"tid":590114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新西選民最撚醒","createTime":"2018-03-12T10:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T14:03:05.000Z","uid":148828,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdf5f4498c1e77172eb1bd1ed78f7f1afd1517e","tid":590114,"uid":148828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"每次都係送最多的反共份子入番去立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2012 立法會選舉 送左6個反共 3個建制番入去（仲要最後一席係良心田少）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2016 補選。迫喊呀頂，推onq岩岩好夠贏10,000票入番去，又俾本土派梁天琦攞6萬票夠上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2016 立法會選舉 又係送左6個反共（其中仲有一個位俾本土派玩下） <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又有智慧地保住長毛岩岩夠票夠贏建制方國珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到2018 補選 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔會亂聽人焦土，識分輕重投范國威（都冇咩拉票都贏到開巷）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港勝在有新東，Proud of 新東 shame on 九西 （先係教主後係姚松炎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n選民黎講新東最撚醒，九西最撚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b8a920a5da1b2b58b17d988e0e98f896597938","tid":590114,"uid":122709,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"標題與內文不符"},{"pid":"869571c937e5cf84125d89879382dce7916b8167","tid":590114,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"新西路過"},{"pid":"4d83c1f74637f4fe08c88bf9173cf5c6a0afafa5","tid":590114,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"新西撚：In Junis Ho we trust！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 